-- Chavez to Name Cilia Flores as Venezuela’s Prosecutor General
-- B y   N a t h a n   C r o o k s
-- 2012-01-31T19:43:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-31/chavez-to-name-cilia-flores-as-venezuela-s-prosecutor-general.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said today that he will name Cilia Flores, the former president
of  Venezuela ’s National Assembly and long-time ally, as the
South American country’s new prosecutor general.  The former prosecutor general,  Carlos Escarra , died of a
heart attack Jan. 25.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nathan Crooks in Caracas at 
 ncrooks@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net  